  "architecture_summary": "InternImage is a large-scale CNN-based foundation model built around an improved deformable convolution operator, DCNv3, combined with transformer-like block designs, stacking rules, and scaling rules. The model uses a 3 × 3 dynamic sparse convolution core with shared weights, multi-group aggregation, and softmax-normalized modulation to support long-range dependencies and adaptive spatial aggregation.",
